'''Ciran''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Cirrus]]. It was shaped like five pointed star and the [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]] described it has having many colorful awnings. The city had two levels, that were linked by [[Turbolift/Legends|turbolifts]]. In [[39 BBY/Legends|39 BBY]], Qui-Gon Jinn, [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]], [[Adi Gallia/Legends|Adi Gallia]], and [[Siri Tachi/Legends|Siri Tachi]] traveled to Ciran to search for [[Talesan Fry]].

